in the front row waiting my turn,

01:52:42.600 --> 01:52:46.020
and I closed my eyes to
concentrate, Smith said,

01:52:46.020 --> 01:52:47.700
"The professor's nervous now.

01:52:47.700 --> 01:52:49.200
He's doing his yoga.

01:52:49.200 --> 01:52:51.770
He's been reading too
much Gary Snyder."

01:52:51.770 --> 01:52:53.070
[ Laughter ]

01:52:53.070 --> 01:52:57.500 position:56%
