01:52:57.500 --> 01:53:00.270
And then it was time to read

01:53:00.270 --> 01:53:04.740
and I chose a political poem
called <i>The Scale </i>published

01:53:04.740 --> 01:53:07.710
in TriQuarterly some years back.

01:53:07.710 --> 01:53:09.440
And I think -- shall
I read it to you?

01:53:09.440 --> 01:53:11.990
Yeah, why not [laughter]?

01:53:11.990 --> 01:53:15.130
This is my 15 minutes of fame.

01:53:15.130 --> 01:53:19.920
The Scale -- and I
read it about this way.

01:53:19.920 --> 01:53:25.250
It wasn't this kind of
highly choreographed reading.

01:53:25.250 --> 01:53:27.540
The man doing life with no chance

01:53:27.540 --> 01:53:30.810
of parole watching
the walls grow visible

01:53:30.810 --> 01:53:35.490
in the first light thinks how
all over the city men wake

01:53:35.490 --> 01:53:39.850
up beside women, even the
losers get lucky sometimes

01:53:39.850 --> 01:53:42.670
but nobody gets lucky here.

01:53:42.670 --> 01:53:44.830
Where they put you to make
sure you have no pleasure

01:53:44.830 --> 01:53:47.120
and miss it constantly.

01:53:47.120 --> 01:53:50.230
The guilt that had seemed
almost nothing inside him,

01:53:50.230 --> 01:53:52.390
they had made solid.

01:53:52.390 --> 01:53:56.910
So they could not look away from it
to take some comfort from the sky

01:53:56.910 --> 01:53:59.910
without seeing bars also.

01:53:59.910 --> 01:54:03.030
It could have been worse.

01:54:03.030 --> 01:54:06.630 position:56%
One hears that in certain countries,
political prisoners are locked

01:54:06.630 --> 01:54:12.910 position:56%
in boxes too short to lie down in,
carried down to a cellar and stacked

01:54:12.910 --> 01:54:17.060
like so many warehouse
crates in one dense tenement

01:54:17.060 --> 01:54:22.030
of tormented flesh soaked
in its own excrement.

01:54:22.030 --> 01:54:26.600
For someone somewhere,
this is actual.

01:54:26.600 --> 01:54:31.280
One of those boxes is where he
is and has to continue being.

01:54:31.280 --> 01:54:34.950
If he dreamed of a prison
cell with a bed and a toilet,

01:54:34.950 --> 01:54:41.200
he would weep bitterly to wake in
his box and find it all a dream.

01:54:41.200 --> 01:54:45.360
This is the stone on the
far pan of the scale.

01:54:45.360 --> 01:54:48.130
Load what you will on the other.

01:54:48.130 --> 01:54:51.170
It scarcely trembles.

01:54:51.170 --> 01:54:54.510
So that was -- it got
me to the second round.

01:54:54.510 --> 01:55:02.250
