that my sample is minuscule.

01:55:44.710 --> 01:55:47.170 position:56%
My methods probably need refinement.

01:55:47.170 --> 01:55:49.240
But at least my questionnaire
was symmetrical

01:55:49.240 --> 01:55:50.660 position:56%
