follow any rational process.

02:02:53.200 --> 02:02:55.340
It doesn't make any
sense but it's powerful.

02:02:55.340 --> 02:02:56.820
It's raw. It's bitter.

02:02:56.820 --> 02:02:59.810
It doesn't seem to me a
false use of language."

02:02:59.810 --> 02:03:04.860
Over and over again, they talk
about being looked by something

02:03:04.860 --> 02:03:07.670
that was opaque to
them for a long time

02:03:07.670 --> 02:03:09.680
